OL,6,FIn stepped Thornbridge Hall, where
OL,7,Fstaff offered to give the locks a new
OL,8,Fhome.
OL,10,FThe two-and-a-half-mile journey was
OL,11,Fnot straightforward, however.
OL,13,FAlex Longsdon, from the estate, said:
OL,14,F"A lorry took them over from Bakwell,
OL,15,Fand to give you an idea of the scale
OL,16,Fof it, it had two relatively flat
OL,17,Ftyres (by the time it arrived)."
