OL,6,FThe locks are currently being stored
OL,7,Fin large industrial sacks, but will
OL,8,Fultimately be displayed on a specially-
OL,9,Fdesigned structure in the estate
OL,10,Fgrounds.
OL,12,FIt will have a water feature and
OL,13,Fseating for visitors.JEstate managing
OL,14,Fdirector Olivia Cridland said the
OL,15,Fresponse to the idea had been
OL,16,F"overwhelmingly positive".
